#### Adding Vibration

The [offical docs](https://developer.android.com/reference/android/os/Vibrator.html) on the Android Vibrator class is a bit sparse, so I got my info from [here](https://stackoverflow.com/a/17066803).

We need to specify that our app uses vibration in the manifest:

<pre><code class="language-xml">
<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.VIBRATE"/>
</code></pre>